trans-unit.source: Provides a listener that routes all tracing and debugging output to the IIS 7.0 infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Fornisce un listener che indirizza tutto l'output di traccia e di debug all'infrastruttura di IIS 7.0.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> class connects the tracing mechanism of [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] to [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Web.IisTraceListener> classe connette il meccanismo di traccia di [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] a [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: This listener class enables developers who create [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applications and who implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> and <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaces to raise page-level, module-level, or handler-level events to the [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastructure when tracing is enabled.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe di listener consente agli sviluppatori che creano [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] applicazioni e che implementano il <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> e <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfacce per la generazione di eventi a livello di pagina, modulo o gestore per il [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] infrastruttura durante la traccia è abilitato.

trans-unit.source: This listener class does not route [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] events to ASP.NET classes.
trans-unit.target: Questa classe listener indirizza [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/includes/iisver-md.md)] eventi alle classi ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: This includes the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class and classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> or <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interface.
trans-unit.target: Ciò include la <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> classe e le classi che implementano il <xref:System.Web.IHttpModule> o <xref:System.Web.IHttpHandler> interfaccia.
